channel.title: Serious problem
channel.description:
[b]This is gone on long enough![/b] [s][s]It's making me mad, and Yes, I HAVE everything downloaded![/s][/s]
Ok, I have been playing MoparScape for awhile now, I was first introduced by my friend bla bla. I started playing 00berscape then I became an admin on it. Now when I go to the webclient it says:"Starting up" Then the whole webclient just exits out all by itself.
So then I downloaded the downloadable version of it then [b]BAM[/b] It just happens again. I downloaded [b]EVERYTHING[/b] need to downloaded such as the newest version of java and JDK and did everything needed. It is continuing to happen, even with the downloaded version. [u]What's the dealio?[/u]
